content:
Hi everyone!

I was mimicking some of the theorems in mathlib, and I saw comments like these:
-- See library note [partially-applied ext lemmas]
-- See note [lower instance priority]

Where can I find these notes? Thank you!
This is a known issue, it will be fixed soon hopefully. You can find all the links to the mathlib3 version (the idea is more or less the same in mathlib4) here.
Jiang Jiedong has marked this topic as resolved.
